               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>Books of Isaiah and Solomon</p>
                     <p>I) መጽሐፈ፡ኢሳይያስ “Book of Isaiah” (fols. <locus from="1r" to="52r"/>), </p>
                     <p>II) ምሳልያተ፡ሶሎሞን “Parables of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="53ra" to="75ra"/>)</p>
                     <p>III) ተግሣፀ፡ሰሎሞን“Admonition of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="71ra" to="75ra"/>)</p>
                     <p>IV) ቃለ፡መክብብ“Word of Ecclesiastes” (fols. <locus from="75ra" to="82va"/>)</p>
                     <p>V) ጥበበ፡ሶሎሞን“Wisdom of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="82va" to="99rb"/>)</p>
                     <p>VI) መኃልየ፡መኃልይ፡ዘሰሎሞን“Song of Songs of Solomon”(fol. <locus from="99va"/>b), incomplete</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                  
               </msContents>
